articles.title: Ashes 1st Test Day 2 Highlights: Khawaja, Carey drive AUS to 311/5 at stumps - Hindustan Times
articles.description: The Ashes 1st Test Day 1 Highlights: Australia 311/5 (U Khawaja 126*, A Carey 52*; S Broad 2/49), trail England (393/8d) by 82 runs at Stumps on Day 2
articles.content: After Day 1, Bairstow said, "Overall it's been a good day. The intent the guys showed, Zak's first shot of the day in stark contrast to last time. The crowd's been on good form and we really enjoyed … [+1123 chars]
